Datasets used in this project are not included in this repository due to size constraints.

Wheat Dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/kushagra3204/wheat-plant-diseases
Rice Dataset:  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/anshulm257/rice-disease-dataset
Sugarcane Dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/akilesh253/sugarcane-plant-diseases-dataset

Custom images collected separately for additional training.